    "description": "<p><strong><u>Company Introduction</u></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Founded in 1979, Chye Joo Construction Pte Ltd is a well-established A1 civil engineering company providing cost-effective and integrated construction and building solutions in the construction industry in Singapore.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We have a varied portfolio of completed projects spanning the public and private sectors. </p>\r\n\r\n<p>We pride ourselves on delivering quality projects on schedule, while not compromising on safety. Customer satisfaction is our topmost priority, and it is the foundation on which we build our business.</p>\r\n\r\n<p> </p>\r\n\r\n<p> </p>\r\n",
